1
00:00:17,393 --> 00:00:18,936
Prethodno u seriji From...

2
00:00:19,019 --> 00:00:22,815
Boyde, ozbiljno ti je u redu
da on uzima ludare

3
00:00:22,898 --> 00:00:25,025
koje je našao u ukletoj šumi?

4
00:00:25,109 --> 00:00:26,652
Ako su odgovori u njegovoj glavi,

5
00:00:26,736 --> 00:00:28,779
moramo ih izvući.
Jesi li spreman za ovo?

6
00:00:28,863 --> 00:00:30,948
Jebeno ne.

7
00:00:31,031 --> 00:00:33,075
Radi golema.

8
00:00:33,159 --> 00:00:34,827
To je div napravljen od gline.

9
00:00:34,910 --> 00:00:36,871
Štiti ljude.
On je zaštitnik.

10
00:00:36,954 --> 00:00:39,582
Ono što sam nosila u sebi,
još uvijek to osjećam.

11
00:00:39,665 --> 00:00:41,417
Djeluje u oba smjera.

12
00:00:41,500 --> 00:00:43,169
Osjeća koliko se bojim.

13
00:00:43,252 --> 00:00:46,964
Ali dok ovo radim, osjećam se snažno.

14
00:00:47,047 --> 00:00:49,675
Mislio sam
da je njegovo žuto odijelo smiješno.

15
00:00:49,759 --> 00:00:51,969
Došao je u autu, kao i svi mi.

16
00:00:52,052 --> 00:00:54,054
Ali nije bio poput nas.

17
00:00:54,138 --> 00:00:56,766
Kad sam našao mamu pokraj
stabla s bocama, vidio sam ga.

18
00:00:58,851 --> 00:01:00,436
Jeo ju je.

19
00:01:00,519 --> 00:01:02,605
Bože moj. Bože.

20
00:01:08,402 --> 00:01:10,613
Ne mogu zamisliti kako joj je.

21
00:01:11,822 --> 00:01:12,740
Čekaj!
-Dolazim!

22
00:01:12,823 --> 00:01:14,074
Ne miči se, u redu?

23
00:01:14,158 --> 00:01:15,576
Gdje te boli?

24
00:01:15,659 --> 00:01:17,036
Ozlijedio sam ruku.

25
00:01:17,119 --> 00:01:19,121
Ovo bi zapravo moglo biti uputstvo

26
00:01:19,205 --> 00:01:21,081
o tome kako spasiti mog tatu.

27
00:01:29,006 --> 00:01:31,759
Sranje! Nije jebeno uspjelo!

28
00:01:31,842 --> 00:01:33,594
Moram pronaći Jezero suza.

29
00:01:33,676 --> 00:01:35,763
Tata mi je rekao da je ovdje.

30
00:01:35,846 --> 00:01:37,848
Možda kad ga nađem, bit će mu bolje.

31
00:01:42,186 --> 00:01:43,646
Mama?

32
00:01:57,243 --> 00:01:59,370
Kažem ti, to su tijela.

33
00:02:00,830 --> 00:02:02,623
Trebali bismo ih izvući.

34
00:02:02,706 --> 00:02:04,124
Jesi li lud?

35
00:02:04,208 --> 00:02:06,335
Nešto ispliva s dna Jezera noćnih mora

36
00:02:06,418 --> 00:02:08,378
i prva stvar koju želiš
napraviti je to izvući na obalu?

37
00:02:08,461 --> 00:02:09,797
Možda ti vodiš stvari

38
00:02:09,880 --> 00:02:12,049
u Kući kolonije, ali ovdje se svi pitamo.

39
00:02:12,132 --> 00:02:14,927
Gledaj, moramo večeras spavati ovdje.

40
00:02:15,010 --> 00:02:17,388
Čak i da sada pobjegnemo,

41
00:02:17,471 --> 00:02:19,473
ne bismo stigli u grad prije mraka.

42
00:02:19,557 --> 00:02:21,809
Ne znam za tebe, ali ja bih
se osjećala puno bolje

43
00:02:21,892 --> 00:02:23,602
da znam tko ili što je

44
00:02:23,686 --> 00:02:26,146
upravo isplivalo na površinu ovog jezera.

45
00:02:26,230 --> 00:02:27,690
U pravu je.

46
00:02:31,360 --> 00:02:33,028
Tiha si.

47
00:02:33,112 --> 00:02:34,655
Što ti misliš?

48
00:02:37,700 --> 00:02:39,368
Izvucimo ih.

49
00:02:41,620 --> 00:02:42,663
Idemo!

50
00:02:56,260 --> 00:02:57,469
Imam ga.

51
00:03:00,514 --> 00:03:01,599
Isuse.

52
00:03:11,066 --> 00:03:12,234
Što sada?

53
00:03:14,153 --> 00:03:16,113
Izvucite to na obalu.

54
00:03:17,239 --> 00:03:18,532
U redu.

55
00:03:39,970 --> 00:03:42,348
Žao mi je što te nismo uspjeli spasiti.

56
00:03:50,272 --> 00:03:52,650
Stvarno sam htio da to bude Jezero suza.

57
00:03:55,486 --> 00:03:56,695
Znam.

58
00:03:59,949 --> 00:04:00,866
Mama?

59
00:04:01,951 --> 00:04:03,243
Da?

60
00:04:03,327 --> 00:04:04,912
Hoćemo li biti dobro?

61
00:04:09,041 --> 00:04:10,417
Nadam se.

62
00:04:23,764 --> 00:04:24,765
Hej, Boyde.

63
00:04:28,644 --> 00:04:29,770
Boyde?

64
00:04:31,271 --> 00:04:33,607
Mislim da su gljive počele djelovati.

65
00:04:34,817 --> 00:04:36,902
Jade?

66
00:04:36,986 --> 00:04:38,737
Malo je direktnije nego što sam očekivao.

67
00:04:40,531 --> 00:04:41,532
U redu.

68
00:04:49,915 --> 00:04:51,332
Isuse!

69
00:04:51,417 --> 00:04:52,459
Sranje!

70
00:04:52,543 --> 00:04:53,585
Jade! Čekaj! Čekaj!

71
00:04:53,669 --> 00:04:56,130
Jade! Jade!
Čekaj! Čekaj! Čekaj! Hej!

72
00:04:56,213 --> 00:04:57,840
Slušaj, nema ničega.

73
00:04:57,923 --> 00:04:59,216
Nema ničega.

74
00:04:59,299 --> 00:05:01,802
Bože.

75
00:05:01,885 --> 00:05:03,345
Ovo možda i nije bila tako sjajna ideja.

76
00:05:06,849 --> 00:05:09,810
Možda da jednostavno... idemo
do Christie i samo...

77
00:05:11,186 --> 00:05:13,897
Ne, ne. Ne. Ne.

78
00:05:13,981 --> 00:05:16,025
Moram ovo napraviti.
Moram to napraviti.

79
00:05:16,108 --> 00:05:18,068
Ali trebam te.

80
00:05:18,152 --> 00:05:21,655
Trebaš mi biti sidro, moj vodič.

81
00:05:21,739 --> 00:05:24,241
Moraš mi reći što je stvarno
a što, znaš, nije.

82
00:05:26,243 --> 00:05:28,537
I trebamo sigurnosnu riječ,
nešto što možeš reći

83
00:05:28,620 --> 00:05:30,539
ako stvari, znaš, izmaknu kontroli;

84
00:05:30,622 --> 00:05:33,250
nešto što će me...
vratiti.

85
00:05:35,169 --> 00:05:36,920
U redu, sigurnosna riječ.

86
00:05:38,213 --> 00:05:39,840
Što će to biti?

87
00:05:46,430 --> 00:05:47,514
Jarac.

88
00:05:48,932 --> 00:05:51,101
Jarac? U redu.

89
00:05:51,185 --> 00:05:52,186
Da.

90
00:05:52,269 --> 00:05:53,645
U redu.

91
00:05:53,729 --> 00:05:55,105
U redu.

92
00:06:00,319 --> 00:06:01,612
Idemo biti čudni.

93
00:06:03,030 --> 00:06:04,031
U redu.

94
00:06:13,624 --> 00:06:15,918
U redu, odakle počinjemo?

95
00:06:16,001 --> 00:06:17,377
Idemo ovim putem.

96
00:06:24,802 --> 00:06:26,929
Samo diši duboko, u redu?

97
00:06:27,012 --> 00:06:28,055
Bit ćeš odlično.

98
00:06:28,138 --> 00:06:30,265
Spreman?
-Čekaj, čekaj, čekaj.

99
00:06:30,349 --> 00:06:31,767
Mo... Možda ovo
ne moramo raditi. Mislim...

100
00:06:31,850 --> 00:06:33,936
možda bismo trebali pričekati.
Ne...

101
00:06:34,019 --> 00:06:36,021
stvarno ne boli ni približno kao prije.

102
00:06:36,105 --> 00:06:38,857
Znam da se bojiš, ali
ako ne namjestimo kost,

103
00:06:38,941 --> 00:06:40,943
nećeš pravilno zacijeliti,

104
00:06:41,026 --> 00:06:43,028
a onda ćemo imati puno veće probleme

105
00:06:43,112 --> 00:06:44,571
nego što ih možemo riješiti ovdje, u redu?

106
00:06:44,655 --> 00:06:45,572
U redu.

107
00:06:45,656 --> 00:06:46,698
U redu.

108
00:06:46,782 --> 00:06:48,826
Samo diši.

109
00:06:48,909 --> 00:06:51,537
U redu.
Idemo na tri.

110
00:06:52,704 --> 00:06:55,332
I trebam da duboko udahneš.

111
00:06:55,415 --> 00:06:56,750
Spreman?

112
00:06:56,834 --> 00:06:57,876
Duboko udahni.

113
00:06:59,378 --> 00:07:01,088
Jedan...

114
00:07:02,381 --> 00:07:04,091
Oprosti. Znam
da je to bio najgori dio.

115
00:07:04,174 --> 00:07:06,093
Samo sam mislila da bi bilo
bolje da to obavimo brzo.

116
00:07:06,176 --> 00:07:07,427
Dobro si.

117
00:07:07,511 --> 00:07:09,388
Imaš li udlagu?

118
00:07:09,471 --> 00:07:11,557
Ne, u ambulanti je.
Odmah se vraćam.

119
00:07:11,640 --> 00:07:12,724
Bio si sjajan.

120
00:07:17,688 --> 00:07:19,398
Hej, ošišala si se.

121
00:07:19,481 --> 00:07:20,774
Lijepo ti stoji.

122
00:07:20,858 --> 00:07:22,568
Hvala.

123
00:07:22,651 --> 00:07:24,027
Duga je to priča.

124
00:10:16,325 --> 00:10:17,409
Lutke su.

125
00:10:20,537 --> 00:10:21,580
Isuse.

126
00:10:37,179 --> 00:10:38,305
Što to radiš?

127
00:10:38,388 --> 00:10:40,557
Provjeravam ima li još iznenađenja.

128
00:11:03,330 --> 00:11:05,540
Zašto bi netko stavio ovo u jezero?

129
00:11:13,423 --> 00:11:14,966
Sranje.

130
00:11:15,050 --> 00:11:16,051
Što?

131
00:11:18,720 --> 00:11:20,680
Mogu se sjetiti samo jednog razloga

132
00:11:20,764 --> 00:11:24,226
zašto ljudi ostavljaju ispunjene lutke
u prirodnoj veličini vani.

133
00:11:26,228 --> 00:11:28,188
Strašila.

134
00:11:28,271 --> 00:11:31,608
Staviš ih u polje da bi otjerao ptice.

135
00:11:33,276 --> 00:11:36,238
Što ako su razlog zašto su bile u jezeru

136
00:11:36,321 --> 00:11:39,157
taj da zadrže nešto drugo dolje...

137
00:11:39,241 --> 00:11:41,326
da ne izađe?

138
00:12:13,066 --> 00:12:14,526
Jesi li dobro?

139
00:12:15,861 --> 00:12:17,821
Da. Dobro sam.

140
00:12:17,904 --> 00:12:19,156
Dobro sam.

141
00:12:19,239 --> 00:12:20,740
Dakle...
I, što sad?

142
00:12:31,418 --> 00:12:33,420
Jade!

143
00:12:33,503 --> 00:12:34,588
Što?

144
00:12:34,671 --> 00:12:36,756
Koji je točno plan?

145
00:12:36,840 --> 00:12:38,717
Što? Da samo hodamo
po šumi po cijeli dan,

146
00:12:38,800 --> 00:12:40,469
čekajući da drveće počne pričati?

147
00:12:40,552 --> 00:12:42,137
Što tražimo?

148
00:12:43,972 --> 00:12:45,182
U pravu si.

149
00:12:46,391 --> 00:12:47,642
U vezi čega?

150
00:12:47,726 --> 00:12:50,103
Nisam postavio pitanje!
Moramo postaviti...

151
00:12:50,187 --> 00:12:53,190
pravo pitanje,

152
00:12:53,273 --> 00:12:55,775
postaviti...
pravu namjeru.

153
00:12:57,486 --> 00:12:58,904
U redu, imam ovo.

154
00:13:02,324 --> 00:13:04,576
Pokaži mi ono što sam znao...

155
00:13:06,828 --> 00:13:08,830
...čega se ne mogu sjetiti.

156
00:13:11,917 --> 00:13:14,794
Pokaži mi što je ovdje unutra
što će nam pomoći da odemo.

157
00:13:21,760 --> 00:13:23,220
Čuješ li to?

158
00:13:24,971 --> 00:13:26,389
Ne.

159
00:13:53,542 --> 00:13:55,043
Bože.

160
00:13:55,126 --> 00:13:57,420
Što nije u redu?
Što vidiš?

161
00:13:58,964 --> 00:14:00,757
Nešto što sam zaboravio.

162
00:14:03,260 --> 00:14:07,973
To sam ja kad sam imao 12 godina.

163
00:14:08,056 --> 00:14:09,099
To je dan kad je umrla moja baka.

164
00:14:11,935 --> 00:14:13,812
Ne razumijem.

165
00:14:13,895 --> 00:14:16,022
Tražila me da joj
sviram, pa sam to i učinio.

166
00:14:16,106 --> 00:14:19,150
Ja...
Svirao sam cijeli dan.

167
00:14:21,194 --> 00:14:23,488
I u jednom trenutku, ja...

168
00:14:23,572 --> 00:14:26,783
Znao sam da ona...

169
00:14:26,866 --> 00:14:29,869
jednostavno više nije bila u sobi.

170
00:14:32,789 --> 00:14:37,627
Ali nisam je mogao pogledati;
samo sam nastavio svirati,

171
00:14:37,711 --> 00:14:41,089
jer sam znao, onog trena kad stanem,

172
00:14:41,172 --> 00:14:43,133
da je stvarno otišla.

173
00:14:43,216 --> 00:14:46,511
Pa sam samo svirao i svirao i svirao.

174
00:14:48,805 --> 00:14:50,181
Prokletstvo! Bože!

175
00:14:50,265 --> 00:14:52,767
Prokletstvo, to nije ono što sam tražio!

176
00:14:52,851 --> 00:14:55,770
Želim se sjetiti
zašto smo zaglavili ovdje!

177
00:14:55,854 --> 00:14:57,314
Želim se sjetiti kako doći kući!

178
00:14:57,397 --> 00:14:58,648
Ne želim ovo!
-Ne, hej,

179
00:14:58,732 --> 00:15:00,233
Jade, Jade, Jade, Jade.

180
00:15:01,401 --> 00:15:03,111
Sve je u redu.

181
00:15:03,194 --> 00:15:04,321
Želim se vratiti.

182
00:15:04,404 --> 00:15:07,991
Samo se želim vratiti!
Želim se vratiti!

183
00:15:08,074 --> 00:15:09,284
Sranje.

184
00:15:10,994 --> 00:15:12,037
Kako si dospio ovamo?

185
00:15:13,663 --> 00:15:14,873
Jade?

186
00:15:16,958 --> 00:15:18,209
Isuse!

187
00:15:18,293 --> 00:15:19,836
Jade?

188
00:15:21,296 --> 00:15:23,381
Pričaj sa mnom.

189
00:15:23,465 --> 00:15:26,176
On... To je tip iz...

190
00:15:30,972 --> 00:15:31,931
Jebote!

191
00:15:32,015 --> 00:15:33,642
Gdje je on?

192
00:15:33,725 --> 00:15:35,518
Kamo je otišao?
Bio je...

193
00:15:35,602 --> 00:15:36,853
Anghkooey.

194
00:15:38,521 --> 00:15:39,481
Jade!

195
00:15:41,066 --> 00:15:42,150
Anghkooey.

196
00:15:43,943 --> 00:15:45,362
Jebeno sam te čuo!

197
00:15:47,238 --> 00:15:49,991
Prestanite.
Prestanite svirati tu pjesmu!

198
00:15:53,787 --> 00:15:55,163
Jade?

199
00:15:56,623 --> 00:15:58,375
Trebat će mi objašnjenje.

200
00:16:01,753 --> 00:16:05,340
Neki seronja kojeg sam vidio
prikovanog na drvetu u naselju

201
00:16:05,423 --> 00:16:07,967
želi da popijem iz iste
lubanje pune krvi koju

202
00:16:08,051 --> 00:16:09,719
vuče sa sobom otkad smo se upoznali!

203
00:16:11,137 --> 00:16:13,223
I stalno ponavlja...
-Anghkooey.

204
00:16:13,306 --> 00:16:15,058
Ne znači li to "sjeti se"?

205
00:16:15,141 --> 00:16:16,142
Da!

206
00:16:16,226 --> 00:16:17,811
Pa, popij to!

207
00:16:19,187 --> 00:16:20,647
Lako tebi reći.

208
00:16:20,730 --> 00:16:22,649
Jade?

209
00:16:22,732 --> 00:16:24,192
Krv nije stvarna.

210
00:16:28,613 --> 00:16:30,573
Pa, izgleda prilično stvarno.

211
00:16:30,657 --> 00:16:34,369
Hej, možda ti pokušava reći
kako da dobiješ svoje odgovore.

212
00:16:37,330 --> 00:16:39,040
Anghkooey.

213
00:16:39,124 --> 00:16:40,083
Nemoj to popiti.

214
00:16:41,501 --> 00:16:42,460
Što?

215
00:16:45,839 --> 00:16:46,715
Jade...

216
00:16:48,508 --> 00:16:49,467
...krv nije stvarna.

217
00:16:50,969 --> 00:16:52,595
Prokletstvo.

218
00:17:14,617 --> 00:17:15,827
Jesi li dobro?

219
00:17:43,855 --> 00:17:48,109
Hej, čekaj, čekaj, čekaj.
Hej! Što je... što je... Jade!

220
00:17:53,782 --> 00:17:54,741
Uđi.

221
00:17:58,161 --> 00:17:59,370
Hej.

222
00:18:02,791 --> 00:18:05,460
Stvarno...

223
00:18:05,543 --> 00:18:07,253
počinjem vidjeti oblik sada.

224
00:18:08,880 --> 00:18:10,006
Trebaš li nešto?

225
00:18:11,800 --> 00:18:13,843
Da, ja...

226
00:18:13,927 --> 00:18:14,969
Samo sam...

227
00:18:17,305 --> 00:18:18,890
Htio sam reći da mi je žao.

228
00:18:20,433 --> 00:18:22,769
Ranije, trebao sam pokušati...

229
00:18:22,852 --> 00:18:25,396
više slušati, umjesto da samo reagiram.

230
00:18:25,480 --> 00:18:28,691
Najjači smo kad podržavamo jedni druge,

231
00:18:28,775 --> 00:18:30,610
a ja to nisam radio.

232
00:18:30,693 --> 00:18:32,695
Uplašio sam se

233
00:18:32,779 --> 00:18:35,573
i trebao sam ti, pružiti podršku.

234
00:18:35,657 --> 00:18:37,575
To je sve.

235
00:18:37,659 --> 00:18:38,743
Hvala ti, Kenny.

236
00:18:44,082 --> 00:18:45,875
Bilo je još nešto?

237
00:18:49,879 --> 00:18:51,714
Sve je u redu, možeš pitati.

238
00:18:52,882 --> 00:18:54,968
Rekla si da si još uvijek
povezana s tom stvari.

239
00:19:00,765 --> 00:19:02,976
Kakav je to osjećaj?

240
00:19:06,062 --> 00:19:09,232
Zastrašujuć...

241
00:19:09,315 --> 00:19:12,360
na način koji ne mogu baš objasniti.

242
00:19:14,112 --> 00:19:15,488
Svake noći, ja...

243
00:19:17,991 --> 00:19:20,118
...idem do tog prozora,

244
00:19:20,201 --> 00:19:21,536
i gledam van,

245
00:19:21,619 --> 00:19:23,746
znajući da ću, jedne od ovih noći,

246
00:19:23,830 --> 00:19:25,248
vidjeti njega kako stoji tamo...

247
00:19:27,083 --> 00:19:28,918
...i bulji u mene.

248
00:19:32,297 --> 00:19:33,798
Što se dogodi onda?

249
00:19:37,468 --> 00:19:38,720
Ne znam.

250
00:19:45,143 --> 00:19:47,687
Slušaj, ako trebaš...
ako trebaš bilo što...

251
00:19:49,314 --> 00:19:50,815
Hvala ti, Kenny.

252
00:20:05,038 --> 00:20:06,789
Henry.

253
00:20:06,873 --> 00:20:08,708
Kenny, hej.

254
00:20:10,460 --> 00:20:11,836
Je li to iz bara?

255
00:20:11,920 --> 00:20:14,297
Da, samo...

256
00:20:14,380 --> 00:20:17,425
držim malu zalihu pri ruci, znaš,

257
00:20:17,508 --> 00:20:20,303
tek toliko da se opustim.

258
00:20:20,386 --> 00:20:21,429
U redu.

259
00:20:21,512 --> 00:20:22,680
Posluži se.

260
00:20:22,764 --> 00:20:24,766
Ne, hvala.
Dobro sam.

261
00:20:36,611 --> 00:20:37,987
Hej.

262
00:20:38,071 --> 00:20:39,530
Zašto ti toliko treba?

263
00:20:43,701 --> 00:20:45,370
Jesi li našla udlagu?

264
00:20:45,453 --> 00:20:46,371
Hej.

265
00:20:48,456 --> 00:20:49,499
Što nije u redu?

266
00:20:53,002 --> 00:20:55,672
Dobro sam.
Da, trebala mi je minuta.

267
00:20:56,798 --> 00:20:57,840
Našla sam ju.

268
00:20:59,676 --> 00:21:01,552
Dobro sam.
-Zlato...

269
00:21:01,636 --> 00:21:02,804
Hej!

270
00:21:02,887 --> 00:21:04,472
Dobro sam, u redu?
-Nisi dobro!

271
00:21:04,555 --> 00:21:06,391
Christie, pusti.
Dobro sam.

272
00:21:06,474 --> 00:21:07,558
Sranje.

273
00:21:14,607 --> 00:21:15,775
Samo, s vremena na vrijeme, ja...

274
00:21:15,858 --> 00:21:17,860
zastanem i razmislim o vrsti stvari

275
00:21:17,944 --> 00:21:19,404
koje su nam postale normalne.

276
00:21:19,487 --> 00:21:22,740
Mislim, sjedimo ovdje,
punimo lutke u prirodnoj veličini

277
00:21:22,824 --> 00:21:25,410
kamenjem jer mislimo da će...

278
00:21:25,493 --> 00:21:28,871
prestani misliti o tome.

279
00:21:28,955 --> 00:21:31,124
Misli na nešto drugo.

280
00:21:31,207 --> 00:21:33,668
Misli o tome kako ćeš se
vratiti svojoj ženi.

281
00:21:33,751 --> 00:21:35,628
Moramo vratiti ova sranja natrag u vodu.

282
00:21:41,551 --> 00:21:43,720
Stvarno misliš da ima nečeg lošeg u vodi?

283
00:21:45,263 --> 00:21:47,515
Mislim da bih radije da ne saznamo.

284
00:21:49,308 --> 00:21:50,393
Hvala.

285
00:22:03,823 --> 00:22:06,576
Tabitha, možeš li mi pomoći s nečim?

286
00:22:08,411 --> 00:22:09,412
Da.

287
00:22:11,998 --> 00:22:13,416
Ovdje.
-Da.

288
00:22:20,882 --> 00:22:24,218
U redu, vidjela sam ti taj izraz na licu.

289
00:22:24,302 --> 00:22:25,762
Što se događa?

290
00:22:27,305 --> 00:22:29,891
Nešto u vezi tih lutaka...

291
00:22:29,974 --> 00:22:31,893
Ne znam, bile su mi poznate.

292
00:22:31,976 --> 00:22:33,394
Ne znam.

293
00:22:33,478 --> 00:22:35,354
Poznate u dobrom ili lošem smislu?
-Ne znam!

294
00:22:35,438 --> 00:22:36,481
Ne... ne znam.

295
00:22:39,150 --> 00:22:41,027
Mislim da sam ih već vidjela.

296
00:22:41,110 --> 00:22:43,946
U redu. Pokušaj, pokušaj se sjetiti.

297
00:22:44,030 --> 00:22:46,574
Pokušavam, Donna!
Poku... pokušavam.

298
00:22:46,657 --> 00:22:49,243
Sve što vidim su, kao, mali
dijelovi i njihova lica i...

299
00:22:49,327 --> 00:22:51,496
To je... Čudno je.

300
00:22:51,579 --> 00:22:55,458
Ima li nečeg u tom jezeru
čega bismo se trebali bojati?

301
00:22:59,253 --> 00:23:01,172
Ne znam.

302
00:23:01,255 --> 00:23:02,882
Spremni smo da ih povučemo natrag unutra.

303
00:23:02,965 --> 00:23:04,383
U redu, idemo.

304
00:23:07,762 --> 00:23:08,930
Samo ih zgrabite.

305
00:23:09,013 --> 00:23:10,056
U redu.

306
00:23:10,139 --> 00:23:11,224
U redu.

307
00:23:13,768 --> 00:23:14,811
Ajmo.

308
00:23:14,894 --> 00:23:15,895
Da.

309
00:23:15,978 --> 00:23:19,148
Oprezno, Patty.
Oprezno.

310
00:23:19,232 --> 00:23:20,149
Da.

311
00:23:21,526 --> 00:23:22,443
Pazi!

312
00:24:03,317 --> 00:24:06,237
Hej...
Hej, što to znači?

313
00:24:06,320 --> 00:24:08,781
Da ću vidjeti stvari
koje ne želim vidjeti?

314
00:24:10,366 --> 00:24:11,325
Hej.

315
00:24:11,409 --> 00:24:13,703
Odgovori mi.

316
00:24:13,786 --> 00:24:16,873
Hej!

317
00:24:21,669 --> 00:24:22,795
Halo?

318
00:24:26,632 --> 00:24:28,009
Hej, Boyde, jesi li...?

319
00:24:30,052 --> 00:24:32,263
Boyde?

320
00:24:32,346 --> 00:24:33,264
Boyde!

321
00:24:34,682 --> 00:24:36,058
Ne radi to.

322
00:24:36,142 --> 00:24:37,935
Nemoj me jebeno tako ostaviti.

323
00:24:38,019 --> 00:24:39,395
Nisam.

324
00:24:39,478 --> 00:24:40,730
Ovdje sam cijelo vrijeme.

325
00:24:42,064 --> 00:24:43,274
Hej...

326
00:24:43,357 --> 00:24:45,443
jesi li dobro?

327
00:24:45,526 --> 00:24:48,237
Da, ja...
ja... ja sam dobro.

328
00:24:48,321 --> 00:24:49,989
Siguran si?

329
00:24:50,072 --> 00:24:51,866
Jade, možemo prestati.

330
00:24:51,949 --> 00:24:53,576
Ako je ovo previše,
još uvijek se možemo vratiti.

331
00:25:00,750 --> 00:25:02,460
Ovuda.

332
00:25:02,543 --> 00:25:04,212
Jade.

333
00:25:04,295 --> 00:25:05,922
Jade!
Sranje.

334
00:25:49,298 --> 00:25:52,510
Boyde...
gdje smo?

335
00:25:54,178 --> 00:25:56,347
Ispred Kuće kolonije smo.

336
00:25:57,807 --> 00:25:59,642
Što vidiš?

337
00:25:59,725 --> 00:26:01,394
Upozorio sam te.

338
00:26:01,477 --> 00:26:05,314
Odgovori koje si tražio dolaze
zamotani u bolne istine.

339
00:26:16,575 --> 00:26:17,743
Tata?

340
00:26:19,036 --> 00:26:21,914
Tata?

341
00:26:21,998 --> 00:26:23,416
M-mislim da to više ne bi trebao gledati.

342
00:26:23,499 --> 00:26:26,294
Ja samo... Ja...

343
00:26:26,377 --> 00:26:28,254
Ja samo...

344
00:26:30,965 --> 00:26:33,759
Što... Što...
Što radiš ovdje...

345
00:26:33,843 --> 00:26:35,094
za... za zabavu?

346
00:26:35,177 --> 00:26:36,595
Što?

347
00:26:36,679 --> 00:26:39,890
Pa, toliko je vremena
u kojem se samo sjedi,

348
00:26:39,974 --> 00:26:42,101
brinut ći hoćeš li preživjeti noć.

349
00:26:42,184 --> 00:26:44,020
Ne smiješ zaboraviti živjeti.

350
00:26:44,103 --> 00:26:48,566
Ti... Moraš živjeti, sine.

351
00:26:48,649 --> 00:26:50,568
Hajde, idemo... idemo...

352
00:26:50,651 --> 00:26:52,069
Pazi!

353
00:26:52,153 --> 00:26:55,156
Ne, dobro sam.
U redu sam. Samo, samo...

354
00:26:55,239 --> 00:26:56,282
Tata?

355
00:26:56,365 --> 00:26:58,034
Samo...

356
00:26:58,117 --> 00:26:59,035
Tata!

357
00:27:03,497 --> 00:27:05,124
Imaš li karte?

358
00:27:05,207 --> 00:27:06,792
Što?

359
00:27:06,876 --> 00:27:09,045
Karte. Za... igranje.
Imaš li karte?

360
00:27:09,128 --> 00:27:10,087
Tata.

361
00:27:10,171 --> 00:27:11,339
Možda u kuhinji.

362
00:27:11,422 --> 00:27:12,381
Što to praviš?

363
00:27:12,465 --> 00:27:14,216
Baš lijepo!

364
00:27:14,300 --> 00:27:15,301
Tata...
-Vidiš?

365
00:27:15,384 --> 00:27:17,178
To je...
dobro za tebe.

366
00:27:17,261 --> 00:27:19,096
Ovi dečki se zabavljaju.

367
00:27:19,180 --> 00:27:20,431
Je li on dobro?

368
00:27:20,514 --> 00:27:21,515
Da.

369
00:27:21,599 --> 00:27:23,809
Radi li ovo?

370
00:27:23,893 --> 00:27:25,811
Pogledaj to.

371
00:27:26,937 --> 00:27:28,230
Možda bi trebao ići prileći.

372
00:27:28,314 --> 00:27:31,442
Prileći? Ne želim
prileći! Želim...

373
00:27:49,335 --> 00:27:51,420
Sjećaš se ove?

374
00:28:00,096 --> 00:28:02,348
Ti... jel' da?

375
00:28:10,815 --> 00:28:11,816
Tata, prestani.

376
00:28:11,899 --> 00:28:14,610
Sjećaš se kad smo svirali?!

377
00:28:15,903 --> 00:28:19,031
Sjedili smo za klavirom i ti bi...

378
00:28:19,115 --> 00:28:21,242
Dao bih ti notu.
To je bila tvoja nota.

379
00:28:21,325 --> 00:28:23,577
I ti...
bio si tako mali!

380
00:28:23,661 --> 00:28:26,163
I... ali tvoja mama,

381
00:28:26,247 --> 00:28:29,375
imala je tako predivan glas.
Sjećaš se?

382
00:28:29,458 --> 00:28:31,252
Tata, molim te.
-Moraš se sjeti...

383
00:28:31,335 --> 00:28:34,130
hajde! Mi... Sjedili bismo tamo
i pričali o tome

384
00:28:34,213 --> 00:28:35,965
kako ćemo jednog dana svi ići oko svijeta

385
00:28:36,048 --> 00:28:39,135
i vidjeti sve te predivne
stvari i bit ćemo...

386
00:28:42,721 --> 00:28:44,723
Hajde!

387
00:29:19,383 --> 00:29:20,426
Hej, Henry, možemo li...?

388
00:29:20,509 --> 00:29:21,510
Ne!

389
00:29:21,594 --> 00:29:23,929
Ne! Ne!

390
00:29:25,389 --> 00:29:28,350
Tko si ti jebote da mi govoriš?

391
00:29:28,434 --> 00:29:31,979
Znaš li što je učinio?

392
00:29:32,062 --> 00:29:33,814
Što je učinio mojoj ženi?

393
00:29:37,902 --> 00:29:38,861
Henry, molim te.

394
00:29:38,944 --> 00:29:40,196
Idemo gore, u redu?

395
00:29:40,279 --> 00:29:42,031
Vic... Vic...
Victore, žao mi je.

396
00:29:42,114 --> 00:29:45,242
Oprosti.
Nisam htio... Ja...

397
00:29:45,326 --> 00:29:47,286
Žao mi je. Žao mi je!

398
00:29:47,369 --> 00:29:49,288
Žao mi je!
-U redu, u redu, u redu!

399
00:29:49,371 --> 00:29:52,249
Žao mi je!
-U redu, idemo... idemo.

400
00:29:52,333 --> 00:29:54,710
Ne. Ne, ti... ti...
ne znaš...

401
00:29:54,793 --> 00:29:57,004
ne znaš što je učinio.

402
00:29:57,087 --> 00:29:58,756
Victore...
pokaži mu sliku.

403
00:29:58,839 --> 00:30:00,758
Pokaži mu sliku onoga što je učinio.

404
00:30:00,841 --> 00:30:04,887
Što nije u redu s tobom?!

405
00:30:04,970 --> 00:30:07,640
Pokaži mu što je učinio!
-U redu, u redu, u redu.

406
00:30:34,416 --> 00:30:37,169
Čemu služi vatra?

407
00:30:37,253 --> 00:30:38,796
Čekaj.

408
00:30:38,879 --> 00:30:41,215
Hoćeš mi reći da
nisi ponijela sljezove kolačiće?

409
00:30:42,967 --> 00:30:44,510
Hoćemo li biti dobro?

410
00:30:46,053 --> 00:30:47,680
Naravno da hoćemo.

411
00:30:47,763 --> 00:30:50,266
Jer ne želim da Julie bude sama.

412
00:30:52,393 --> 00:30:54,812
Znaš što,

413
00:30:54,895 --> 00:30:58,065
prvo što ćemo ujutro napraviti,
ustat ćemo,

414
00:30:58,148 --> 00:31:02,236
uzeti stvari i
bježati odavde. U redu?

415
00:31:04,113 --> 00:31:05,489
Hajde.

416
00:31:05,573 --> 00:31:06,490
Uđi u kolibu.

417
00:31:09,201 --> 00:31:11,036
Sviđa mi se kad si ovdje.

418
00:31:12,037 --> 00:31:13,914
Jednostavno nije tako strašno
kad si ti u blizini.

419
00:31:25,676 --> 00:31:27,094
Randall.

420
00:31:27,177 --> 00:31:30,055
Slušaj... Slušaj.

421
00:31:30,139 --> 00:31:32,141
Onaj jedini put kad si
pokušala napraviti nešto

422
00:31:32,224 --> 00:31:35,936
što bi zapravo dokazalo
da je stvarno, nije uspjelo!

423
00:31:36,020 --> 00:31:38,647
Ovdje se ne radi o meni ni o straničniku.

424
00:31:38,731 --> 00:31:41,442
U redu? Radi se o tebi i tvom
strahu od onih ruševina.

425
00:31:41,525 --> 00:31:42,693
Jesi li ozbiljna?

426
00:31:42,776 --> 00:31:44,361
Ti si jebena kukavica, Randall.

427
00:31:44,445 --> 00:31:46,071
A ti si tvrdoglavo malo dijete

428
00:31:46,155 --> 00:31:48,324
koje ne zna što joj je,
jebote, pred nosom.

429
00:31:48,407 --> 00:31:50,701
Stvarno?
A što je to?

430
00:31:50,784 --> 00:31:52,411
Ovo mjesto te jebe u mozak

431
00:31:52,494 --> 00:31:54,288
jer zna koliko ti nedostaje tata!

432
00:31:56,081 --> 00:31:59,585
Ne. U krivu si.

433
00:31:59,668 --> 00:32:02,212
Gledao sam te kako imaš
dva napadaja u dva dana.

434
00:32:02,296 --> 00:32:04,423
U redu? Doslovno
si pržiš vlastiti mozak.

435
00:32:04,506 --> 00:32:06,300
Pa, zašto mi ne kažeš što je vjerojatnije:

436
00:32:06,383 --> 00:32:08,385
da putuješ kroz poglavlja priče

437
00:32:08,469 --> 00:32:10,638
ili da ćeš jednog od ovih dana,
imati napadaj

438
00:32:10,721 --> 00:32:12,222
koji neće prestati?
-Nije me briga!

439
00:32:12,306 --> 00:32:13,766
To je rizik koji sam spremna preuzeti!

440
00:32:15,351 --> 00:32:17,353
Onda si moron.

441
00:32:17,436 --> 00:32:20,064
A da je tvoj tata sada ovdje,
bio bi jebeno zapanjen

442
00:32:20,147 --> 00:32:22,191
koliko si prokleto glupa.

443
00:32:23,484 --> 00:32:25,319
Sada si ljuta na mene
samo zato što znaš da sam u pravu.

444
00:32:38,707 --> 00:32:39,750
Dobro sam.

445
00:32:39,833 --> 00:32:41,335
Očito nisi dobro.

446
00:32:41,418 --> 00:32:43,504
U redu, imala sam trenutak, to je sve!

447
00:32:43,587 --> 00:32:45,631
To je bilo puno više od
samo trenutka, Marielle!

448
00:32:45,714 --> 00:32:47,841
U redu, znači, ovo mjesto
te nikada prije nije slomilo?

449
00:32:47,925 --> 00:32:49,343
Bože moj!
-Stvarno?

450
00:32:49,426 --> 00:32:51,470
Nije ti trebala samo minuta
da jebeno pošiziš?

451
00:32:51,553 --> 00:32:53,597
To nije velika stvar.

452
00:32:53,681 --> 00:32:55,641
Mari!
-Pusti to, Christie!

453
00:32:57,017 --> 00:32:58,060
Oprosti.

454
00:32:58,143 --> 00:32:59,061
U redu je.

455
00:33:13,325 --> 00:33:16,286
Mari!

456
00:33:45,899 --> 00:33:48,318
Što vidiš?

457
00:33:48,402 --> 00:33:51,155
To su ljudi iz mojih halucinacija.

458
00:33:51,238 --> 00:33:52,990
Zašto su ovdje?

459
00:33:53,073 --> 00:33:54,825
Zašto su svirali tu pjesmu?

460
00:33:56,243 --> 00:33:57,703
Znaš zašto.

461
00:34:04,793 --> 00:34:06,420
Svi oni su ja.

462
00:34:09,757 --> 00:34:11,425
To su bili životi koje sam ovdje živio.

463
00:34:15,053 --> 00:34:17,723
Neki od njih...
i još mnogi drugi.

464
00:34:17,806 --> 00:34:20,141
Pogledaj ih pažljivo.
Što vidiš?

465
00:35:11,944 --> 00:35:14,321
Nitko od njih nije rastrgan.

466
00:35:17,282 --> 00:35:19,827
Nisu ih ubila...
stvorenja u šumi!

467
00:35:21,787 --> 00:35:23,914
Ovi ljudi su ubijeni.

468
00:35:26,875 --> 00:35:27,793
Tko ih je ubio?

469
00:35:29,503 --> 00:35:30,754
Znaš tko.

470
00:35:35,300 --> 00:35:37,302
Male ribe u mreži morskog psa?

471
00:35:37,386 --> 00:35:38,804
Što to...

472
00:35:40,722 --> 00:35:43,058
Bože moj.

473
00:35:43,141 --> 00:35:44,852
Ubili su ih ljudi u gradu.

474
00:35:44,935 --> 00:35:46,562
Što?
Jade, s kim pričaš...

475
00:35:46,645 --> 00:35:48,063
Samo... daj mi...

476
00:35:48,146 --> 00:35:49,815
Uvijek je isto.

477
00:35:49,898 --> 00:35:53,527
Kad jednom saznaju istinu
o tome tko si ti,

478
00:35:53,610 --> 00:35:56,697
da si ti taj kojeg su djeca dozivala,

479
00:35:56,780 --> 00:35:58,490
prvo, krive tebe,

480
00:35:58,574 --> 00:36:01,118
onda te mrze,

481
00:36:01,201 --> 00:36:02,744
i na kraju te ubiju.

482
00:36:06,415 --> 00:36:07,624
A Tabitha?

483
00:36:09,167 --> 00:36:10,586
Za Tabithu je gore.

484
00:36:10,669 --> 00:36:12,337
Ali, gledaj...

485
00:36:15,257 --> 00:36:19,261
Ako svaki put umrem...

486
00:36:19,344 --> 00:36:20,679
što to govoriš?

487
00:36:20,762 --> 00:36:21,972
Želiš reći da nema puta kući?

488
00:36:22,055 --> 00:36:24,975
Kako...
Kako ovo pomaže?

489
00:36:25,058 --> 00:36:27,352
Kako da spriječim
da se to dogodi ovaj put?

490
00:36:31,607 --> 00:36:32,816
Odgovori mi!

491
00:36:32,900 --> 00:36:34,443
Jade. Hej, Jade. Jade.

492
00:36:41,575 --> 00:36:44,661
U redu, idemo ga povući ovamo.

493
00:36:44,745 --> 00:36:46,121
Dobro?

494
00:36:47,539 --> 00:36:49,625
U redu.
Dva, tri.

495
00:36:50,751 --> 00:36:52,127
U redu.

496
00:36:54,046 --> 00:36:54,963
U redu.

497
00:36:57,424 --> 00:36:59,426
Hoćeš li biti dobro, Victore?

498
00:36:59,509 --> 00:37:01,136
Da.
Ja ću se pobrinuti za njega.

499
00:37:10,354 --> 00:37:13,273
Hej, Victore.
O čemu...

500
00:37:13,357 --> 00:37:14,900
O čemu je pričao?

501
00:37:27,746 --> 00:37:30,374
Čovjek u žutom odijelu...

502
00:37:30,457 --> 00:37:32,084
pojeo je moju majku.

503
00:37:34,795 --> 00:37:37,047
Ali nisam mu to nikada trebao reći.

504
00:37:59,111 --> 00:38:00,028
Halo?

505
00:38:04,866 --> 00:38:06,493
Kamo je dovraga otišao?

506
00:38:06,576 --> 00:38:09,496
Hej, možemo li stati na minutu?

507
00:38:09,579 --> 00:38:11,039
Zašto si, jebote, pričao o tome

508
00:38:11,123 --> 00:38:12,332
da te ljudi ubijaju tamo?

509
00:38:17,087 --> 00:38:18,046
Hej.

510
00:38:21,800 --> 00:38:23,051
Ovamo.

511
00:38:32,978 --> 00:38:35,605
Što radimo?
Zašto smo dolje?

512
00:38:42,154 --> 00:38:43,071
Hej!

513
00:38:46,033 --> 00:38:47,701
Hej!
-Pomozi mi!

514
00:38:47,784 --> 00:38:48,869
Pomozi mi! Hajde!

515
00:39:00,756 --> 00:39:02,215
Boyde...

516
00:39:03,842 --> 00:39:05,552
vidiš li vrata u tom zidu?

517
00:39:07,721 --> 00:39:08,930
Da.

518
00:39:23,487 --> 00:39:25,363
Izvolite.

519
00:39:25,447 --> 00:39:26,656
Hvala ti, Sophia.

520
00:39:36,291 --> 00:39:38,710
Možeš li nam pokušati reći što se
dogodilo u ambulanti?

521
00:39:41,463 --> 00:39:42,547
Radio se upalio.

522
00:39:44,299 --> 00:39:46,843
U redu. I...?

523
00:39:48,637 --> 00:39:51,181
Čula sam ih kako vrište.

524
00:39:51,264 --> 00:39:52,808
Koga?

525
00:39:54,184 --> 00:39:55,727
Sve.

526
00:39:56,728 --> 00:39:59,606
Svaku pojedinu osobu
koja je ikada ovdje umrla.

527
00:39:59,689 --> 00:40:04,027
Tako je bilo meni kad smo bili u komori.

528
00:40:04,111 --> 00:40:07,405
Sve što sam čula,
sve što sam osjećala bila je...

529
00:40:07,489 --> 00:40:10,450
patnja svake pojedine
osobe koja je ovdje ikada umrla.

530
00:40:15,831 --> 00:40:17,707
Govorila sam sebi da to nije stvarno,

531
00:40:17,791 --> 00:40:19,459
da ne može biti.

532
00:40:20,710 --> 00:40:23,380
Ali kad se radio upalio,
kao da je sva ta bol

533
00:40:23,463 --> 00:40:27,050
i užas ponovno prošla kroz mene.

534
00:40:29,136 --> 00:40:30,679
Ti si prorok.

535
00:40:34,141 --> 00:40:35,392
Što?

536
00:40:35,475 --> 00:40:38,979
Možda te Bog odabrao
da čuješ njihovu patnju.

537
00:40:41,314 --> 00:40:43,024
U redu, ne mogu ovo.

538
00:40:43,108 --> 00:40:44,484
Mari...
-Ne.

539
00:40:44,568 --> 00:40:46,528
Mari, čekaj.
Samo...

540
00:40:46,611 --> 00:40:47,654
čekaj.

541
00:40:50,907 --> 00:40:53,034
Vidjela sam već da se ovo događa ovdje.

542
00:40:54,619 --> 00:40:56,705
Ovo mjesto, ulazi ljudima u glavu i...

543
00:40:56,788 --> 00:40:58,707
Ovo je drugačije, Christie.

544
00:41:00,375 --> 00:41:03,044
Ovdje ima nečeg starog,

545
00:41:03,128 --> 00:41:05,881
nečeg... drevnog.

546
00:41:08,592 --> 00:41:11,344
I hrani se našom patnjom i ne prestaje.

547
00:41:12,971 --> 00:41:16,516
Čak i nakon što umremo,
još smo uvijek zarobljeni ovdje.

548
00:41:18,643 --> 00:41:20,312
I nikada nećemo otići.

549
00:41:30,447 --> 00:41:33,742
Ponekad zaboravim da je samo dijete.

550
00:41:33,825 --> 00:41:36,995
Uvijek se činio tako odraslim.

551
00:41:37,078 --> 00:41:38,538
Uvijek je bio takav.

552
00:41:40,332 --> 00:41:42,834
Jim ga je znao zvati mali profesor.

553
00:41:44,461 --> 00:41:47,881
Tako znatiželjan i pun pitanja.

554
00:41:47,964 --> 00:41:50,091
Možda on može shvatiti
što je u tom prokletom jezeru.

555
00:41:50,175 --> 00:41:51,426
Prestani!

556
00:41:53,178 --> 00:41:54,554
Oprosti.

557
00:41:56,014 --> 00:41:58,308
Koliko još do izlaska sunca?

558
00:41:58,391 --> 00:42:00,769
Pet minuta manje nego
kad je netko zadnji put pitao.

559
00:42:02,604 --> 00:42:04,522
Samo pokušaj malo odspavati.

560
00:42:04,606 --> 00:42:06,900
Šališ se, zar ne?

561
00:42:06,983 --> 00:42:10,278
Sve što moramo učiniti
je izdržati do jutra.

562
00:42:10,362 --> 00:42:12,030
Tada možemo otići k vragu odavde

563
00:42:12,113 --> 00:42:15,075
i vratiti se u noćnu moru koju razumijemo.

564
00:42:16,117 --> 00:42:17,911
Imamo dugu šetnju ujutro, pa...

565
00:42:26,169 --> 00:42:27,545
Koji je to vrag?

566
00:42:39,599 --> 00:42:40,976
Tabitha?

567
00:42:43,186 --> 00:42:46,231
Znam taj zvuk.

568
00:42:53,488 --> 00:42:54,906
Lutke...

569
00:42:54,990 --> 00:42:57,409
bile su manje.

570
00:42:57,492 --> 00:43:00,078
Bile su moje.
Igrala sam se s njima.

571
00:43:00,161 --> 00:43:01,079
O čemu ona priča?

572
00:43:03,999 --> 00:43:04,916
Mama?

573
00:43:06,876 --> 00:43:08,420
Čovjek; bio je ljut.

574
00:43:10,797 --> 00:43:12,215
Došao je i uzeo mi ih.

575
00:43:12,299 --> 00:43:14,676
Rekao je da mu zadaju noćne more,

576
00:43:14,759 --> 00:43:16,469
pa ih je bacio u jezero.

577
00:43:20,390 --> 00:43:22,600
Ali jednog dana, čovjek je umro,

578
00:43:22,684 --> 00:43:26,396
i njegove noćne more...

579
00:43:26,479 --> 00:43:28,356
njegove noćne more su izašle iz jezera.

580
00:43:31,776 --> 00:43:33,111
Bože moj, Donna, moramo ići.

581
00:43:33,194 --> 00:43:35,322
Moramo ići odmah.
-Tabitha, ne možemo.

582
00:43:35,405 --> 00:43:37,198
Donna! Ne, ne razumiješ!
Ne razumiješ!

583
00:43:37,282 --> 00:43:38,658
Nismo sigurni ovdje!
Ne možemo ostati ovdje.

584
00:43:38,742 --> 00:43:40,118
Ne, imamo talisman na vratima.

585
00:43:40,201 --> 00:43:42,495
Ne, ne, ne, talismani nas neće
zaštititi, ne od ovog!

586
00:43:42,579 --> 00:43:44,831
Kako znaš to? Kako,
jebote, znaš išta od toga?!

587
00:43:44,914 --> 00:43:45,832
Hej, hej, hej.

588
00:43:47,042 --> 00:43:49,336
Idemo! Idemo! Bježi!

589
00:43:49,419 --> 00:43:52,464
Idi, idi!
Hajde, idi!

590
00:43:52,547 --> 00:43:54,215
Ethan!
-Idi! Izlazi!

591
00:43:58,762 --> 00:44:01,014
Hej! Silazi s njega!

592
00:44:14,152 --> 00:44:15,278
Donna!

593
00:44:15,362 --> 00:44:16,196
Ellis!

594
00:44:17,697 --> 00:44:19,115
Gdje je Patty?

595
00:44:19,199 --> 00:44:20,575
Ona... Nije s tobom?

596
00:44:20,658 --> 00:44:21,910
Ne!

597
00:44:21,993 --> 00:44:23,244
Sranje!

598
00:44:23,328 --> 00:44:25,789
Ellis!
-Donna, molim te!

599
00:44:37,008 --> 00:44:37,967
Mama!

600
00:44:38,051 --> 00:44:39,260
Sve je u redu.

601
00:44:49,145 --> 00:44:50,980
Ne!

602
00:44:59,447 --> 00:45:00,949
Hej! Hajde!

603
00:45:02,117 --> 00:45:04,536
Moramo ići! Idi!

604
00:45:07,622 --> 00:45:09,124
Moramo trčati.

605
00:45:09,207 --> 00:45:11,000
Bez obzira na to što se dogodi,
moramo nastaviti...

606
00:45:11,084 --> 00:45:12,085
Donna!

607
00:45:12,168 --> 00:45:13,211
Donna!
-Donna!

608
00:45:13,294 --> 00:45:14,838
Donna, ne!
-Donna!

609
00:45:37,527 --> 00:45:38,778
Hej.

610
00:45:40,321 --> 00:45:41,865
Donna? Jesi li dobro?

611
00:45:41,948 --> 00:45:43,867
Da. Da, da.

612
00:45:45,368 --> 00:45:47,871
Whoa!

613
00:45:51,166 --> 00:45:52,750
Što se upravo dogodilo?

614
00:45:54,544 --> 00:45:56,629
Sjetila sam se.

615
00:45:56,713 --> 00:45:58,631
Sjetila sam se kako ih povrijediti.

616
00:46:59,192 --> 00:47:00,777
Jebeno...

617
00:47:00,860 --> 00:47:02,362
Isuse!

618
00:47:03,821 --> 00:47:05,532
Boyde!

619
00:47:09,702 --> 00:47:11,829
Tko si ti, jebote?

620
00:47:16,209 --> 00:47:17,210
U redu.

621
00:47:26,052 --> 00:47:27,470
Što je ovo?

622
00:47:32,267 --> 00:47:33,935
U redu...

623
00:48:09,220 --> 00:48:10,096
Sranje.

624
00:48:11,639 --> 00:48:13,474
Boyde? Boyde?!

625
00:48:15,727 --> 00:48:17,020
Boyde?

626
00:48:18,146 --> 00:48:19,480
Hej!

627
00:48:19,564 --> 00:48:21,065
Hej, Jade,

628
00:48:21,149 --> 00:48:22,483
moramo ići.

629
00:48:22,567 --> 00:48:24,736
Ne možemo biti ovdje dolje.

630
00:48:24,819 --> 00:48:26,696
Ali ovo nije stvarno!
Ovo ne može biti stvarno!

631
00:48:26,779 --> 00:48:27,697
Jade!
-Što?

632
00:48:27,780 --> 00:48:29,073
Slušaj me.

633
00:48:29,157 --> 00:48:31,117
Jarac. U redu?

634
00:48:31,200 --> 00:48:33,494
Jarac.
Ovo je stvarno.

635
00:48:33,578 --> 00:48:37,165
Tražio si da ti budem sidro,
pa me jebeno slušaj.

636
00:48:37,248 --> 00:48:39,042
Ne, Boyde.
Samo smo u Kući kolonije.

637
00:48:39,125 --> 00:48:40,376
Tuneli nisu ovako blizu.

638
00:48:40,460 --> 00:48:41,878
Blizu?

639
00:48:41,961 --> 00:48:43,921
Hodali smo niz taj jezivi hodnik...

640
00:48:44,005 --> 00:48:45,089
ovo prestaje sad!

641
00:48:45,173 --> 00:48:46,132
Idemo.

642
00:48:46,215 --> 00:48:48,051
U redu. U redu.

643
00:48:48,134 --> 00:48:49,510
U redu. Dobro.

644
00:48:49,594 --> 00:48:50,928
Hej!

645
00:48:51,012 --> 00:48:53,681
Odvući ću te odavde
ako jebeno budem morao!

646
00:48:53,765 --> 00:48:55,767
U redu. Dobro. U redu.

647
00:49:23,878 --> 00:49:26,422
Ovo je mjesto gdje su žrtvovana djeca.

648
00:49:40,603 --> 00:49:42,105
Kako nas to saznanje vodi kući?

649
00:49:47,026 --> 00:49:50,530
Tabitha i ja, već smo ih pokušali spasiti.

650
00:49:50,613 --> 00:49:52,824
Pokušali smo toliko puta.

651
00:49:52,907 --> 00:49:55,118
Je li... je li...
ima li nečega ovdje?

652
00:49:55,201 --> 00:49:57,954
Ima li nečega, nečega što trebamo?

653
00:49:58,037 --> 00:50:00,540
Reci mi kako da ih spasimo
kad već nismo uspjeli!

654
00:50:05,920 --> 00:50:07,839
Bok, Jade.

655
00:50:13,886 --> 00:50:15,263
Trebao si slušati Boyda.

656
00:50:15,346 --> 00:50:16,639
Ne!

657
00:50:16,723 --> 00:50:18,391
Ali nikad zapravo nisi
bio pametan, zar ne?

658
00:50:24,897 --> 00:50:27,108
Ne! Ne!
Ne, ne, ne, ne!

659
00:50:27,191 --> 00:50:28,651
Ne, ne, ne!

660
00:50:28,735 --> 00:50:30,445
Ne! Ne!

661
00:50:32,488 --> 00:50:34,824
Skini se, jebote, s mene!

662
00:50:42,039 --> 00:50:43,833
Ne, ne!

663
00:50:43,916 --> 00:50:44,876
Silazi!

664
00:50:44,959 --> 00:50:46,210
Ne!

665
00:50:47,920 --> 00:50:49,338
Anghkooey.

666
00:50:55,428 --> 00:50:57,722
Jade! Jade!
Hej, hej, hej!

667
00:50:57,805 --> 00:50:59,182
Jesi li dobro?

668
00:50:59,265 --> 00:51:00,767
Jesi dobro?

669
00:51:00,850 --> 00:51:02,769
Što mi jebeno radimo ovdje?

670
00:51:02,852 --> 00:51:04,437
Što?
-Kako smo dospjeli ovamo?

671
00:51:04,520 --> 00:51:06,314
Što... Što? Hej.

672
00:51:06,397 --> 00:51:07,899
Kako smo jebeno dospjeli ovamo?!

673
00:51:07,982 --> 00:51:11,486
Jade, nikad nisi ni otišao.

674
00:51:11,569 --> 00:51:14,155
Ne, ne, ne.
Bili smo u tunelima.

675
00:51:14,238 --> 00:51:16,824
Ne, sjediš ovdje već satima.

676
00:51:16,908 --> 00:51:20,536
Bio si na prozoru...

677
00:51:20,620 --> 00:51:21,954
sjeo si,

678
00:51:22,038 --> 00:51:23,956
i to je to.
Ti...

679
00:51:24,040 --> 00:51:27,293
Ne, ne, ne.
Ne, ne.

680
00:51:27,376 --> 00:51:29,462
Bilo je još toga. Bilo je...

681
00:51:29,545 --> 00:51:30,963
Bilo je puno više toga.

682
00:51:36,385 --> 00:51:37,720
Znam gdje su.

683
00:51:37,804 --> 00:51:38,971
Što?

684
00:51:42,809 --> 00:51:44,477
Znam što moramo učiniti da idemo kući.

685
00:51:46,521 --> 00:51:48,523
Znam kako možemo spasiti djecu.
